TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This source qualifier transformation is used to read the records from gross_margin_ppk and gross_margin table.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_GROSS_MARGIN_PPK

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select g.fiscal_year, g.fiscal_period, g.item_id, sum(g.dollars) dollars, sum(case when cost_measure_name is not null then g.garments else 0 end) c_garments, sum(case when sales_measure_name is not null then g.garments else 0 end) d_garments, sum(g.adj_extended_cost_dollars) adj_extended_cost_dollars from gross_margin_ppk g where fiscal_year =(select d.cy_year_yyyy-1 as PY from slba.day_dimension d where d.day_date=trunc(sysdate)) and g.INVOICED_QUALITY_CODE in ('1','6') AND g.gross_margin_ind ='Y' and (g.cost_measure_name = 'OS COGS' or g.sales_measure_name ='Gross OS') group by g.fiscal_year, g.fiscal_period, g.item_id having (sum(case when cost_measure_name is not null then g.garments else 0 end) + sum(case when sales_measure_name is not null then g.garments else 0 end) ) !=0

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This union transformation is used to join the records from both gross_margin and gross_margin_ppk tables.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: UN_GM_GMPPK

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This source qualifier transformation is used to read the records from gross_margin table.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_GROSS_MARGIN

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select fiscal_year, fiscal_period, item_id, sum(g.dollars) dollars, sum(case when cost_measure_name is not null then g.garments else 0 end) c_garments, sum(case when sales_measure_name is not null then g.garments else 0 end) d_garments, sum(g.adj_extended_cost_dollars) adj_extended_cost_dollars from gross_margin g where fiscal_year =(select d.cy_year_yyyy-1 as PY from slba.day_dimension d where d.day_date=trunc(sysdate)) and G.INVOICED_QUALITY_CODE in ('1','6') AND g.gross_margin_ind ='Y' AND nvl(g.ppk_indicator,'N') = 'N' and (g.cost_measure_name = 'OS COGS' or g.sales_measure_name ='Gross OS') group by fiscal_year, fiscal_period, item_id having (sum(case when cost_measure_name is not null then g.garments else 0 end) + sum(case when sales_measure_name is not null then g.garments else 0 end) ) !=0

TRANSFORMATION.NAME: AGG_DOLLARS
